	<text>
		<body xml:lang="en">
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_002334_0001"/><!--pb/@n='76r'-->
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>Burnbank Road</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>Hamilton</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right">9<hi rend="sup">th</hi> June 1865</p>
<lb/><p>My Dear <persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Murray</persName></p>
<lb/><p><persName>Madame Hocede</persName>
<lb/>'s fee is Â£120 per 
<lb/>annum - she says 
<lb/>that Music Masters 
<lb/>charge from ten to 
<lb/>twenty francs an 
<lb/>hour - German 
<lb/>masters generally 
<lb/>five. What <unclear cert="medium">washing</unclear>
<lb/>may come to 
<lb/>I don<reg>'</reg>t know 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_002334_0002"/><!--pb/@n='76v'-->
<lb/>but I shall get 
<lb/>more accurate 
<lb/>information by &amp; 
<lb/>bye.</p>
<lb/><p><persName>Sir Roderick<reg>'</reg>s</persName>
<lb/>name may go out 
<lb/>of the Dedication<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>He liked it himself 
<lb/>but I shall explain 
<lb/>and he will not 
<lb/>object. You had 
<lb/>better expunge 
<lb/>it &amp; send it to 
<lb/>press. I send 
<lb/>the last sheet 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_002334_0003"/><!--pb/@n='77r'-->
<lb/>all correct, <hi rend="underline">through</hi>
<lb/><persName>Oswell</persName> to <hi rend="underline">Press</hi>.</p>
<lb/><p>I am going to pay 
<lb/>a promised visit 
<lb/>to some friends 
<lb/>at <persName>D<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Daubeny's</persName>
<lb/>Oxford next 
<lb/>week &amp; will call 
<lb/>either going or 
<lb/>coming<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p>Could you <choice><sic>recal</sic><corr>recall</corr></choice>
<lb/>a note book 
<lb/>lent for the 
<lb/><placeName>Rovuma</placeName> wood 
<lb/>cut &amp; leave it 
<lb/>for me where 

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_002334_0004"/><!--pb/@n='77v'-->
<lb/>I could get it? I need it 
<lb/>for returning to that 
<lb/>River.</p>
<lb/><p rend="center">I am &amp;c </p>
<lb/><p>David Livingstone</p>
<lb/><p>Do you know if there 
<lb/>is any truth in the 
<lb/>reported resignation 
<lb/>of <persName>Sir Bartle Frere</persName>
<lb/>in the Times. His 
<lb/>departure would 
<lb/>be a grievous loss 
<lb/>to me in Bombay.</p>
			
</div>
